      <div class="project-list animate">
         <div class="row">
            <div class="col six">
               <h3 style="margin-top: .3em;"> Microservice based Marketplace </h3>
               <div class="row project-text">
                  <div class="col three">
                    <p>
                      An E-marketplace for products, where customer can browse the inventory and purchase the item.
                     <ul>
                         <li>Customer can browse the inventory (without login)</li>
                         <li>Customer can add the item to cart (without login)</li>
                         <li>Customer can checkout to purchase (login required)</li>
                         <li>Customer can see his/her purchase history (login required)</li>
                         <li>Customer can see his/her profile (login required)</li>
                     </ul>
                    </p>

                     <table style="width:100%;">
                       <tr>
